<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Ghost Stories</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The infamous Ghost Stories dub, was a result of the dubbing company ADV, having been given mostly free reign to do whatever they wanted with it, as along as it sold well. The result was a nearly purely comedic dub, filled with raunchy, adult jokes and improv taken to eleven.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="4e5bmd">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
